Document: aras
Title: ARAS - A Radio Automation System
Author: Martintxo
Abstract: ARAS is a suite of programs for a radio automation system. Some ARAS features are:
 * It reads mp3, wav, ogg, mod, xm and other media formats.
 * It can play files or media streams over internet.
 * Highly configurable.
 * Log file capability.
 * Time signal capability.
 * Interval signal capability.
 * It works with single file blocks, playlist blocks, blocks of random files, block of one random file and interleaved blocks.
 * Fade out capability.
Section: Sound

